{"tid":1715144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有片證明前日交通警講大話 — 佢絕對無受到任何襲擊而開車撞人","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:51:38.000Z","uid":123774,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abbeb6881784b16794222495552ddab1e97f68e8","tid":1715144,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"前日4點警謊：<br />\n<br />\n「警察公共關係科總警司謝振中在記者會上表示，當時有警員被示威者用化學品噴面，感到痛楚，及短暫失去視力，鐵騎警試圖分隔雙方但被襲擊」<br />\n<br />\n有片大家睇 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>手足又係好似筲箕灣咁<br />\n攤開雙手叫黑警冷靜</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B4yYSioFNno/?igshid=i0kl4h7ne0gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB4yYSioFNno%2F%3Figshid%3Di0kl4h7ne0gk&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLafG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=cae570e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B4yYSioFNno/?igshid=i0kl4h7ne0gk</a><br />\n<br />\n成班情緒失控搵市民發洩嘅曱甴<br />\n日日四點出嚟講大話<br />\n唔係有片都唔會認<br />\n你讀書再少做人都應該有少少廉恥"},{"pid":"133a127d176ec010cec93aa56a11eeca6794fbb9","tid":1715144,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a1290c654ede102f27449655aeea64e25c6f9ee","tid":1715144,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c402c440281ad954686a9cabae6181b584fa3f1","tid":1715144,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dfc459b397ffd8ea24a6a2dacf523b34ebac891","tid":1715144,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f65f986590ebbabef51182d7e6a53ae294bbc581","tid":1715144,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e6873fe6c434269c408b09901f4378b72de4fb54","tid":171514